    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Overview\nWhen POST to /support-chat, this workflow handles support:\n\n1. Normalize input\n2. Lookup store in Postgres\n3. Build WooCommerce auth\n4. Run GPT-4o-mini agent\n5. Parse reply and escalate flag\n6. Notify human via Gmail if needed\n7. Route to webchat/WhatsApp/email\n8. Return success ack",
        "height": 296,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "d0b8559b-9a5a-4f86-b6d2-46c7c0e856f8",
      "name": "Note: Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1536,
        400
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Node-by-node Purpose\n\n1. Customer Message In\nReceives POST webhook\n\n2. Normalize Input\nExtracts channel, message, email, phone\n\n3. Lookup Store Config\nQueries Postgres for store\n\n4. Build Auth Context\nCreates WooCommerce auth header\n\n5. Store Found?\nChecks if store exists\n\n6. Support Agent\nGPT-4o-mini handles order queries\n\n7. Parse Agent Output\nGets reply, intent, escalate\n\n8. Escalate?\nDecides if human needed\n\n9. Notify Human Support\nSends Gmail to team\n\n10. Channel Router\nPicks webchat, WhatsApp, email\n\n11. Success Ack\nReturns JSON response",
        "height": 532,
        "width": 456,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "63886076-ccb7-4911-943a-f2dad2c38caf",
      "name": "Note: Node-by-node",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        640,
        208
      ]
    }
